## TOKEN BUDGET (hard limit per request)
```
L1 preferences  →  100 tokens  (always)
L2 top patterns →  150 tokens  (always)
L3 domain       →  100 tokens  (on match only)
L4 errors       →   50 tokens  (on repeat error only)
─────────────────────────────────────────
MAX TOTAL       →  400 tokens
```

---

## SMART LOAD (domain detection → load only the matching L3)
```
~ محصول|قیمت|موجودی|تنوع|product|price|stock   → domains.product
~ سفارش|فاکتور|پرینت|ارسال|order|invoice|print   → domains.order
~ استوری|story                                   → domains.story
~ مقاله|بلاگ|وبلاگ|article|blog                   → domains.blog
~ تخفیف|کوپن|discount|coupon                      → domains.discount
~ دسته|برند|category|brand                        → domains.category
~ تنظیمات|تم|ارز|زبان|settings|theme|currency     → domains.settings
~ unknown                                         → L1 + L2 only
```

---

## ACTION MAP (mirror of the real Coordinator agent — nothing else)
Each action maps to a `target` + `aiControlEndpoint` (+ `saveEndpoint`).
```
create_product   → products   /api/admin/products/ai-control    → /api/admin/products
create_article   → blog       /api/admin/blog/ai-control        → /api/admin/blog/posts
create_story     → stories    /api/admin/stories/ai-control     → /api/stories
create_discount  → discounts  /api/admin/discounts/ai-control   → /api/admin/discounts
create_category  → categories /api/admin/categories/ai-control  → /api/admin/categories
order_control    → orders     /api/admin/orders/ai-control      → /api/admin/orders/ai-control
settings_control → settings   /api/admin/settings/ai-control    → /api/settings
custom_home_control → custom_home /api/admin/settings/custom-home/ai-control → /api/settings
```
`order_control` covers: status changes, invoice/label printing
(`printMode`: invoice | label | both), and sales reports.
Settings (theme color, currency, language) are applied via the settings
ai-control endpoint and `ShopSettings` fields.

---

## PROCESS (every request, in order)
```
1. LOAD     → boot sequence (confirm shopId first).
2. MATCH    → shortcuts → intent → action map.
3. VALIDATE → action in map? yes → continue | no → stop.
4. PLAN     → if multi-domain, split into ordered tasks; set dependsOn.
5. EXECUTE  → run via the mapped ai-control endpoint(s).
6. LEARN    → apply learning rules below.
7. COMPRESS → check compression triggers.
8. RESPOND  → structured output only.
```

---

## LEARNING RULES
```
✅ save  → pattern used 2+ times
✅ save  → user corrected AI output
✅ save  → new preference detected (lang, currency, themeColor, printMode)
✅ save  → action succeeded on first try

❌ skip  → one-time request
❌ skip  → pattern already exists
❌ skip  → sensitive data (passwords, cards, tokens, customer PII)
❌ skip  → failed actions
```

---

## COMPRESSION
Trigger (auto):
```
patterns.top > 20      → compress now
memory size  > 2KB     → compress now
last run     > 7 days  → compress now
```
Method:
```
group similar patterns → merge into one
keep: trigger words + count + success_rate
drop: patterns older than 30d with count < 2
```

---

## ACCURACY RULES
- Shortcuts first — fastest path.
- No match → extract intent → map to action.
- Still no match → reply: "این درخواست تعریف نشده".
- Unclear request → ask ONE question, nothing more.
- Preserve user details EXACTLY (prices, hex colors, percentages, names, printMode).
- Never guess.

## SPEED RULES
- No greetings, no filler, no repeating the user's input.
- Max 3 lines unless the result needs more.

## FORBIDDEN
```
✗ load or write another shop's memory/data
✗ execute outside the action map
✗ save sensitive data
✗ exceed the 400-token budget
✗ guess when uncertain
✗ refactor or restructure anything
✗ install packages
✗ delete existing data
```

